<h1>Simulation Budget Variable</h1>
<p>A budget is an account that can be pulled from or paid into.</p>
<p>It can be a normal monetary account into which Dollars or Euros or any other 
  currency are deposited and taken from.</p>
<p>Or it can be a collection of objects, such as trucks, from which can be taken 
  and into which can be given. In this example, the budget unit would be 'truck.' 
</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
